[Student "S"]
{When partner shows 17+ points with his Reverse you are sure you belong in game. Since he did not support your \Ss you know he doesn't have four of them. You also know you have an 8-card fit in \Ds, but surely nine tricks in Notrump will be easier than eleven in \Ds.}

